77
00:03:14,709 --> 00:03:17,989
But they still heavily manage its exchange
rate.

78
00:03:17,989 --> 00:03:20,579
They control how much it can change each day,

79
00:03:20,579 --> 00:03:22,299
and buy and sell foreign currency

80
00:03:22,299 --> 00:03:24,109
